                        </origin>
                        <provenance>
                            <p>According to the colophon on <locus from="8v" to="8v" scheme="folios"/> (and notes on <locus from="SL1r" to="SL1r" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="Ir" to="Ir" scheme="folios"/>) the text was written by <persName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/person/100672">Ericus Nicolai</persName> in <placeName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/place/100089">Uppsala</placeName>. The fate of the text after this is unknown. The note on <locus from="LCI" to="LCI" scheme="other"/> states that the manuscript belonged to the <orgName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/org/100059">Antiquities Archive</orgName>.</p>
                        </provenance>
                        <acquisition>
                            <p>From the <orgName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/org/100059">Antiquities Archive</orgName> to the <orgName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/org/100004">National Library</orgName> in <date cert="low" when="1780">1780</date>.</p>
                        </acquisition>
